                    <label auto.number="yes" denominator="yes"/>
                    <para>
                      <text>The person appointed or elected in accordance with the Head of State Referenda Act <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">2009</citation></changeable> will be New Zealand’s head of State.</text>
