          <para>
            <text>Omit from sections 17, 18, 20, and 21 “Her [<emphasis style="italic">or</emphasis> His] Majesty [<emphasis style="italic">specify the name of the reigning Sovereign, as thus:</emphasis> Queen Elizabeth the Second], Her [<emphasis style="italic">or</emphasis> His] heirs and successors” and substitute “New Zealand”.</text>
